lead_paragraph: Raptors center Bismack Biyombo faces a suspension for a potential Game 7 of the Eastern Conference finals after picking up a flagrant foul in the first quarter of Game 6 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Raptors' Biyombo Faces Game 7 Suspension After Flagrant Foul
